Installation:

    git clone git://github.com/nelstrom/dotvim.git ~/.vim

Create symlinks:

    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
    ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

Vundle setup:

    git clone https://github.com/gmarik/vundle.git ~/.vim/bundle/vundle
    
    Launch vim and run :PluginInstall and you good to go!
    
    Note that vim plugin "youCompleteMe" needs some configuration, 
    check it's documentation and configure it as per your needs.
